\id TDX - Mato Scripture
\ide UTF-8
\h Haruanga Sabangadi
\toc1 Haruanga Sabangadi Mana Urana Xuanoa Urana bila li Urana Tibura bila li Urana Garanoa, Yesu Kristo, bila li Urana Aningonoa bila li Urana tongtongia axamang longgalo Urana wasa mana axamang longgalo Lipudi bila li Lipu longgalo dilibu kubolu diandi Bungina lipudi dilibu kubolu diandi, ding bila li Lipudi dihixiya ba Urana xapdi muli nam daxap salaga Urana xap lipudi muli bila li Murung sibuna mana lipu longgalo, saing bo ba xapdi muli Yesu Kristo mati bu xap kira muli Yesu sibinoa damia kubolura diandi, binabu tawa haruangia te Urana yunga kubolura diandi Urana libu kira tamaring maxania Urana sina walinga hauna nakira Urana libu kira tasok garandi Urana bo ba xap kira muli, binabu taria baru? Tausinga kubolura diandi, saing talibudi muli te Tahatum haringina mana Yesu bu xap kira muli Tatiti Urana Xuanoa bu taxabia mana Urana Taxap langa Tagugunia rangua lipu hatuminga haringinam teladi Tagugunia rangua lipu hatuminga haringinamdi, saing taxang Toxoratamona Angiang Hatuminga Haringinama Tahaxa walingaria bila li Tasu mana Urana haruanganoa, xaung Toxoratamona kiria Yesu Kristo Murura sibuna mana Urana xaung lipudi Kuboluradi bing bila Kristo kubolundi Tasabu Taharua xai sibuna na Urana bunging xumana Tahauli teladi Tatatua kira Talibu mana siang xaung xalaxaladi bila li Tatuba ba tala haruangia te, nabu kira sanga Tawa hawa mana gabmandi Tasabu mana babudiu tai Tahanania asaxadiu tai Takinu rangua yaungamdiu tai, xaung talibu kubolu miaxuamau tai Kakahara mana lang haringinau tai Sabungua bila li Sabunga bakbagindi bing bila li Sabunga yanamindi tamogudi bing lipua na bila li Sabunga yanamindi walingadingdi bing bila li Tawa hawa mana sabunga yanamindi Bakbakdi bing bila li Neng mondi bing bila li Garadi bing bila li Baudingtibudingdi bing bila li Tapdi bing bila li Labu tataxiti yaunguau tai Mauxangandi daxap Kristo lipuxindi Taxauxau mana mauxangandi daxap kira Taxauxau mana taxap salaga Tamaxuwa mana matiyua Urana wa haxek rangua kira, saing hauli kira Satan bo ba hanggalangia kira Urana sina haringingua nakira bu tasoxauti Satan xaung tadali mauxangandi Bunging xumana Urana hamaringia lipu busingamdi Baraxintadi bagula disok kimu Yesu bagula goxoya ma titia Urana bagula suxuya lipu longgalo Yesu Kristo rimania Adi Urana xapdi muli bagula duwa long xaiya Adi Urana xapdi muli te bagula duwa long salakkamia Haruanga Sabangadi Disu Mana Xusungangadi Ubo ba uxabia mana Urana? Ubo ba uxabia mana Urana Garanoa Yesu Kristo? Uhatum ba Urana wasa maung te? Uhatum ba ulibu kubolu dian tela te? Uhatum ba Urana bagula yunga kubolum diandi te? Murum mana Yesu Kristo xapkung muli? Hatumingam luwa mana oxop walinga subingang teguama? Ubo ba uxabia ba usabu kimbo tegu? Ubo ba uxabia mana baraxintadi daxai mana usabu mana? Mauxangandi tubaikdi daxapkung? Ubusi? Umaxuwa mana umati? Ubo ba uxabia mana Kristo lipuxing kubolunoa? Ubo ba uxabia mana kubolu baruamtadi didoa? Uxunumia ba sanga ba uhaxa walingamia bila Urana muruna mana te? Oxop salaga namua na ung Kristo lipuxinoa? Uhatum ba heku ugugunia rangua lipu hatuminga haringinam teladi? Lipu tela libu doa maung? Uyau? Tubaiga xapkung bila ubo ba ukinu rangua tela uyau mana te? Garam? Baumtibumdi duwauyu? Ubagu lipu tela raxap mana haulingua? Tubaiga xapkung ubo ba bila ulibu kubolu diana? Ulibu kubolu diana? Umaxuwa mana Satan kimbo xaungandi? Atim disala mana lipu tela? Uhasua maung saing uiti yama? Uharua diana? Tubaiga xapkung bila ubo ba ulangua? Lipudi dibo ba kakaham lang haringinia ranguadi? Uhatum mana xalingimdi buk? Lipudi dibo ba usabu mana babudi? Ubo ba uxabia ulibu kubolu baruamtadi na yanamimdi?
\toc2 Haruanga Sabangadi
\mt1 Haruanga Sabangadi Mana Urana Xuanoa
\mt2 Urana bila li
\mt3 Urana Tibura bila li
\p Mak 10:27, 12:29-30; Luk 1:37, 6:35-36; Yon 4:23-24; Aposel 14:14-17, 17:22-31; Rom 1:18-23, 11:33-36; 1 Korin 8:4-6; 2 Korin 1:3; 1 Timoti 1:17, 6:15-16; Hibru 4:13, 10:30-31; Yems 1:17; 1 Pita 1:14-17; 1 Yon 1:5, 4:7-12, 4:16; Yut 24-25; Hatanga Masok 4:8-11, 15:3-4.
\mt3 Urana Garanoa, Yesu Kristo, bila li
\li1 • Yesu Kristo Urana Garanoa
\li2 Matyu 11:27-30, 16:13-17; Luk 1:35; Yon 1:1-18, 5:19-29, 6:35-40, 8:58, 11:25-27, 14:5-11, 17:1-5, 20:26-31; Aposel 3:13-16, 4:10-12; Rom 1:3-4; 1 Korin 3:11; 2 Korin 4:4-6, 5:21; Galesia 4:4-5; Pilipai 2:5-11; Kolosi 1:15-20, 2:9-10; Hibru 1:1-14, 7:26-28; 1 Yon 2:1-2, 5:20; Hatanga Masok 1:12-18, 19:11-16.
\li1 • Sok lipu saing haing tela hayau
\li2 Yon 1:14; Luk 1:26-38; Matyu 1:18-25; Luk 2:1-20; Matyu 2:1-23; Galesia 4:4-5; Pilipai 2:6-7; Hibru 2:14-18.
\li1 • Tubatuba lipudi saing hamaringia lipu busingamdi
\li2 Matyu 4:23-25, 7:28-29, 9:35-36, 11:1-6; Luk 4:14-44; Aposel 10:36-38, Yon 20:30-31.
\li1 • Libu axamang haringing xumana
\li2 Matyu 8:1-4, 8:5-13, 8:14-15, 8:23-27, 8:28-33, 9:1-7, 9:18-26, 9:27-31, 9:32-33, 12:9-14, 12:22, 14:15-21, 14:22-32, 15:22-28, 15:32-38, 17:14-18, 20:29-34, 21:18-22; Mak 1:21-28, 7:32-37, 8:22-25; Luk 5:4-8, 7:11-15, 13:10-13, 14:1-4, 17:12-14, 22:50-51; Yon 2:1-11, 4:46-54, 5:5-9, 9:1-7, 11:11-44, 21:4-6; Aposel 2:22.
\li1 • Yuda yanamindi dituxu saing daharua ba bing mati
\li2 Matyu 26:47-68, 27:1-2, 27:11-31; Mak 14:43-65, 15:1-20; Luk 22:47-53, 22:63-71, 23:1-25; Yon 18:1-14, 18:19-24, 18:28–19:16.
\li1 • Digoxi xai balingamia
\li2 Matyu 27:32-56; Mak 15:21-41; Luk 23:26-49; Yon 19:17-37.
\li1 • Dikimang
\li2 Matyu 27:57-66; Mak 15:42-47; Luk 23:50-56; Yon 19:38-42.
\li1 • Mesa muli saing lipu teladi dibagu
\li2 Matyu 28:1-20; Mak 16:1-8; Luk 24:1-49; Yon 20:1–21:14; Aposel 1:3-8, 2:24-32, 3:15, 4:10, 4:33, 10:39-43, 13:29-39, 17:2-3, 17:30-31; Rom 1:4, 4:24-25; 1 Korin 15:3-8, 15:12-21; Hatanga Masok 1:18.
\li1 • Goxoya mala long xaiya
\li2 Luk 24:50-51; Aposel 1:9-11, 2:32-36, 5:30-31; Rom 8:34; Epasas 1:20-23; Pilipai 2:9-11; Hibru 1:3-11, 2:9, 4:14-16, 7:25-26, 10:12-14; 1 Pita 3:22.
\mt3 Urana Aningonoa bila li
\p Matyu 28:19; Mak 1:9-11, 3:28-30; Luk 1:35, 3:16, 4:1, 11:13, 12:12 Yon 1:32-34, 3:5-8, 7:37-39, 14:15-17, 14:26, 15:26, 16:7-15, 20:19-23; Aposel 1:4-5, 1:8, 2:1-18, 2:38-39, 4:31, 5:3-5, 8:14-17, 10:44-48, 13:2-4, 15:28, 16:7-10, 19:1-7; Rom 5:5, 7:6, 8:9-16, 8:26-27; 1 Korin 2:4, 2:9-16, 3:16, 6:11, 6:19, 12:1-13; 2 Korin 1:21-22, 5:5, 13:14; Galesia 3:2-5, 4:6, 5:16-18, 5:22-25; Epasas 1:13-14, 1:17, 3:16, 4:3-4, 4:30, 5:18-20, 6:17-18; 1 Tesalonaika 1:5-6, 5:19; 2 Tesalonaika 2:13; Taitas 3:5-6; Hibru 2:4, 9:14; 1 Pita 1:2, 1:11; 2 Pita 1:20-21; 1 Yon 2:20, 3:24, 4:13, 5:6-8.
\mt3 Urana tongtongia axamang longgalo
\p Matyu 19:4; Yon 1:3; Aposel 14:15, 17:24-26; 1 Korin 8:6; Kolosi 1:15-16; Hibru 1:2, 11:3; Hatanga Masok 4:11.
\mt3 Urana wasa mana axamang longgalo
\p Matyu 6:25-34, 10:29-31; Aposel 14:15-17; Rom 8:28, 11:36; Kolosi 1:17; Hibru 1:3; Yems 4:13-16.
\mt2 Lipudi bila li
\mt3 Lipu longgalo dilibu kubolu diandi
\p Yon 8:7-9; Rom 3:9-20, 3:23, 5:12; Galesia 3:22; 1 Yon 1:8-10.
\mt3 Bungina lipudi dilibu kubolu diandi, ding bila li
\p Rom 1:18-32, 8:5-8; Galesia 5:19-21; Epasas 2:1-3, 5:3-5; Kolosi 3:5-10; Yems 4:17; 1 Pita 4:3; 1 Yon 3:4-5.
\mt3 Lipudi dihixiya ba Urana xapdi muli nam daxap salaga
\p Matyu 10:28, 13:41-42; Yon 3:18-20, 3:36; Aposel 17:30-31; Rom 1:18-19, 6:23; Galesia 6:7-8; Kolosi 3:5-6; 2 Tesalonaika 1:7-9; Hibru 9:27, 10:26-31; 1 Pita 1:17, 4:3-5; Yut 7; Hatanga Masok 20:11-15.
\mt2 Urana xap lipudi muli bila li
\mt3 Murung sibuna mana lipu longgalo, saing bo ba xapdi muli
\p Yon 3:16; Rom 5:8; 1 Timoti 2:3-6; 2 Pita 3:9; 1 Yon 4:9-10.
\mt3 Yesu Kristo mati bu xap kira muli
\p Mak 10:45; Yon 3:16; Rom 4:25, 5:8; 1 Korin 15:3-4; 2 Korin 5:19-21; Galesia 3:13; 1 Timoti 2:5-6; Hibru 2:9, 9:28; 1 Pita 1:18-20, 2:24-25, 3:18; 1 Yon 2:2; Hatanga Masok 5:8-10.
\mt3 Yesu sibinoa damia kubolura diandi, binabu tawa haruangia te
\p Matyu 26:26-29; Rom 3:25, 5:9-10; Epasas 1:7; Hibru 9:11-14; 1 Yon 1:6-7; Hatanga Masok 7:14-17.
\mt3 Urana yunga kubolura diandi
\p Aposel 5:31, 10:43, 26:18; Epasas 1:7, 4:32; Kolosi 1:13-14, 2:13-14; Hibru 10:17-18; 1 Yon 1:8-10.
\mt3 Urana libu kira tamaring maxania
\p Aposel 13:38-39; Rom 1:16-17, 3:21-26, 5:1, 5:18-19; Galesia 2:16, 3:6-9; Taitas 3:7.
\mt3 Urana sina walinga hauna nakira
\p Yon 3:1-16, 5:19-29, 10:10, 11:25-26, 14:6, 17:2-3, 20:31; Rom 5:21, 6:5-14, 8:10-17; 2 Korin 5:17; Galesia 2:20; Epasas 2:1-6; Kolosi 2:13, 3:1-4; 2 Timoti 1:10; Taitas 3:4-7; 1 Pita 1:23; 1 Yon 5:11-13.
\mt3 Urana libu kira tasok garandi
\p Yon 1:12-13; Rom 8:14-17; Galesia 4:6-7; Hibru 12:5-11; 1 Yon 3:1-3.
\mt2 Urana bo ba xap kira muli, binabu taria baru?
\mt3 Tausinga kubolura diandi, saing talibudi muli te
\p Matyu 4:17; Mak 6:12; Luk 13:1-5, 15:1-31, 24:45-47; Aposel 2:37-40, 3:19-20, 17:29-31, 20:21, 26:19-20; 2 Korin 7:8-11; 2 Pita 3:9; Hatanga Masok 9:20-21.
\mt3 Tahatum haringina mana Yesu bu xap kira muli
\p Yon 1:12, 3:15-18, 3:36, 6:47, 14:6, 20:31; Aposel 4:12, 16:30-31; Rom 3:20-22, 10:9-10; Galesia 2:16; Epasas 2:8-9.
\mt3 Tatiti Urana Xuanoa bu taxabia mana Urana
\p Matyu 4:1-4, 5:17-20, 22:29; Yon 8:31-32, 20:31; Aposel 20:32; Rom 15:4, 16:26; Kolosi 3:16; 1 Tesalonaika 2:13; 1 Timoti 4:13; 2 Timoti 3:14-17; Hibru 4:12; 1 Pita 1:22-25; 2 Pita 1:19-21; 2 Yon 9-10; Hatanga Masok 1:3.
\mt3 Taxap langa
\p Matyu 28:18-20; Yon 3:22, 4:1-2; Aposel 2:37-42, 8:12, 8:36-38, 10:44-48, 16:14-15, 16:31-33, 19:1-7, 22:12-16; Rom 6:1-4; Galesia 3:26-27; Kolosi 2:12; 1 Pita 3:20-22.
\mt3 Tagugunia rangua lipu hatuminga haringinam teladi
\p Matyu 18:19-20; Aposel 2:41-47; Rom 12:4-8; Epasas 1:22-23, 4:11-16; Kolosi 3:15-17; 1 Timoti 4:13; Hibru 10:24-25.
\mt3 Tagugunia rangua lipu hatuminga haringinamdi, saing taxang Toxoratamona Angiang Hatuminga Haringinama
\p Matyu 26:26-30; Mak 14:22-26; Luk 22:14-20; 1 Korin 10:14-22, 11:17-34.
\mt2 Tahaxa walingaria bila li
\mt3 Tasu mana Urana haruanganoa, xaung Toxoratamona kiria Yesu Kristo
\p Yon 14:15, 14:21, 14:23-24, 15:10-17; Rom 13:8-10; 1 Pita 1:14-16; 1 Yon 2:3-8, 3:22-24; 2 Yon 5-6.
\mt3 Murura sibuna mana Urana xaung lipudi
\p Matyu 5:43-48, 22:34-40; Mak 12:28-34; Luk 10:25-37; Yon 13:34-35, 14:21, 15:12-17; Rom 12:9-10, 13:8-10; 1 Korin 13:1-3, 16:14; Galesia 5:13-15; 1 Tesalonaika 4:9-10; 1 Pita 1:8, 4:8; 1 Yon 2:9-11, 3:11-18, 4:7-21, 5:3.
\mt3 Kuboluradi bing bila Kristo kubolundi
\p Yon 13:34-35, 14:27; Rom 12:9-13; Galesia 5:22-26; Kolosi 3:12-17; 1 Tesalonaika 5:16-18.
\mt3 Tasabu
\li1 • Tasabu baru?
\li2 Matyu 6:5-13, 7:7-11, 18:19-20; Mak 11:24-25; Luk 11:1-13, 18:1-8, 21:36; Yon 14:13-14, 15:7, 16:23-26; Rom 8:26-27, 12:12; Epasas 2:18, 6:18; Pilipai 4:6-7; Kolosi 4:2; 1 Tesalonaika 5:17; 1 Timoti 2:1-4, 2:8, 4:4-5; Hibru 4:16, 10:19-22; Yems 1:5-8, 4:2-3, 5:13-18; 1 Pita 4:7; 1 Yon 3:21-22, 5:14-15.
\li1 • Babu mana lipudi disabu baru
\li2 Matyu 11:25-26, 14:23, 19:13-15; Mak 1:35; Luk 5:16, 6:12, 22:32, 22:39-46; Yon 11:41-42, 17:1-26; Aposel 4:24-31, 16:25, 20:36, 21:5; Rom 1:9-10, 10:1-2, 15:30-33; 2 Korin 12:7-10; Epasas 1:15-20, 3:14-21, 6:19-20; Pilipai 1:3-5, 1:9-11; Kolosi 1:9-12, 4:3-4; 1 Tesalonaika 3:9-13; 2 Tesalonaika 1:11-12, 3:1-5; Hibru 5:7, 7:25.
\mt3 Taharua xai sibuna na Urana bunging xumana
\p Luk 17:11-19; Yon 6:11; Rom 1:21; Epasas 5:20; Pilipai 4:4-7; Kolosi 2:7, 3:17, 4:2; 1 Tesalonaika 5:18; 1 Timoti 2:1, 4:4-5.
\mt3 Tahauli teladi
\p Matyu 6:1-4, 7:12, 25:31-46; Luk 3:10-11, 6:38; Aposel 11:27-30; 1 Korin 10:24; 2 Korin 8:1-15, 9:1-15; Galesia 6:9-10; Pilipai 4:14-19; Hibru 10:24, 13:1-3, 13:16; Yems 1:27, 2:15-16; 1 Yon 3:16-18.
\mt3 Tatatua kira
\p Matyu 5:3-12, 18:1-5; Luk 14:7-11, 18:9-14; Epasas 4:2; Pilipai 2:3-11; Kolosi 3:12-13; Yems 4:5-10; 1 Pita 5:5-7.
\mt3 Talibu mana siang xaung xalaxaladi bila li
\p Matyu 6:19-21, 6:24-34; Luk 12:13-21, 12:32-34; Aposel 20:35; 1 Timoti 6:6-10, 6:17-19; Hibru 13:5-6; Yems 2:1-9, 5:1-6.
\mt3 Tatuba ba tala haruangia te, nabu kira sanga
\p Matyu 5:25-26, 5:38-42, 18:15-17; Rom 12:14-21; 1 Korin 6:1-8.
\mt3 Tawa hawa mana gabmandi
\p Matyu 22:15-22; Aposel 5:27-29; Rom 13:1-7; 1 Timoti 2:1-4; Taitas 3:1; 1 Pita 2:13-17.
\mt3 Tasabu mana babudiu tai
\p Matyu 4:10; Aposel 17:22-31; 1 Korin 5:11, 6:9-11, 8:1-13, 10:1-22; 2 Korin 6:14-18; Galesia 5:19-21; 1 Tesalonaika 1:9-10; 1 Yon 5:21; Hatanga Masok 21:8, 22:15.
\mt3 Tahanania asaxadiu tai
\p Matyu 9:13; Mak 12:33; Rom 12:1; Hibru 9:6–10:18.
\mt3 Takinu rangua yaungamdiu tai, xaung talibu kubolu miaxuamau tai
\p Matyu 5:27-30; Yon 8:2-11; Rom 13:8-10; 1 Korin 5:9-11, 6:9-20; Galesia 5:19; Epasas 5:3; Kolosi 3:5-6; 1 Tesalonaika 4:1-8; Hibru 13:4; Yut 7.
\mt3 Kakahara mana lang haringinau tai
\p Rom 13:13; 1 Korin 5:11, 6:9-11; Galesia 5:19-21; Epasas 5:18; 1 Timoti 3:1-3; Taitas 1:7; 1 Pita 4:3-5.
\mt2 Sabungua bila li
\mt3 Sabunga bakbagindi bing bila li
\p Matyu 16:13-20; Aposel 2:41-42; Rom 12:4-8; 1 Korin 12:12-30; Epasas 1:22-23, 2:19-22, 4:1-16; Kolosi 1:18; Hibru 10:24-25; 1 Pita 2:4-10; Hatanga Masok 19:5-10.
\mt3 Sabunga yanamindi tamogudi bing lipua na bila li
\p Aposel 6:1-6; Aposel 14:23; 1 Timoti 3:1-13; Taitas 1:5-9.
\mt3 Sabunga yanamindi walingadingdi bing bila li
\p Matyu 28:18-20; Luk 22:24-27; Aposel 20:17-35; 1 Tesalonaika 2:1-12; 1 Timoti 4:1-16, 2 Timoti 2:1-26, 3:10-17, 4:1-5; Taitas 2:7-8; 1 Pita 5:1-4.
\mt3 Tawa hawa mana sabunga yanamindi
\p 1 Korin 9:14; Galesia 6:6; 1 Tesalonaika 5:12-13; 1 Timoti 5:17-22; Hibru 13:7, 13:17.
\mt2 Bakbakdi bing bila li
\mt3 Neng mondi bing bila li
\p Matyu 19:4-6; 1 Korin 7:1-16; Epasas 5:21-33; Kolosi 3:18-19; Taitas 2:3-5; Hibru 13:4; 1 Pita 3:1-7.
\mt3 Garadi bing bila li
\p Matyu 15:3-6; Luk 2:51; Epasas 6:1-3; Kolosi 3:20; 1 Timoti 5:4, 5:8; Hibru 12:7-11.
\mt3 Baudingtibudingdi bing bila li
\p Epasas 6:4; Kolosi 3:21; 1 Timoti 3:4-5.
\mt3 Tapdi bing bila li
\p Aposel 6:1; Rom 7:2-3; 1 Korin 7:39-40; 1 Timoti 5:3-16; Yems 1:27.
\mt3 Labu tataxiti yaunguau tai
\p Matyu 5:31-32, 19:3-9; Luk 16:18; Rom 7:2-3; 1 Korin 7:10-16.
\mt2 Mauxangandi daxap Kristo lipuxindi
\mt3 Taxauxau mana mauxangandi daxap kira
\p Rom 8:18-25, 8:28; 2 Korin 1:4, 4:16-18; Yems 1:2-4; 1 Pita 1:6-9, 2:19-21, 5:8-10.
\mt3 Taxauxau mana taxap salaga
\p Matyu 5:10-12; Mak 13:9-13; Luk 12:4-9; Yon 15:18-21, 16:1-4; Aposel 5:41; Rom 8:35-37, 12:12-14, 12:17-21; 1 Korin 4:11-13; 2 Korin 4:8-11, 12:10; Pilipai 1:28-29; 2 Tesalonaika 1:4-8, 3:2-4; 2 Timoti 3:10-13; Hibru 10:32-39, 12:3-4; 1 Pita 3:13-17, 4:12-19; Hatanga Masok 2:10.
\mt3 Tamaxuwa mana matiyua
\p Yon 6:39-40, 11:17-27, 14:1-4; Rom 8:10-11, 8:38-39, 14:7-9; 1 Korin 15:12-58; 2 Korin 5:1-10; Pilipai 1:20-24; 1 Tesalonaika 4:13-18; Hibru 2:14-15; Hatanga Masok 14:13, 21:1-4, 22:1-5.
\mt3 Urana wa haxek rangua kira, saing hauli kira
\p Matyu 18:19-20, 28:19-20; Yon 14:16-23; Rom 8:35-39; 2 Korin 6:16-18; Epasas 3:17-19; Pilipai 4:13; Kolosi 2:6-7; 2 Tesalonaika 3:16; Hibru 13:5-6.
\mt3 Satan bo ba hanggalangia kira
\p Matyu 13:19; Luk 4:1-13, 22:3-4; Yon 8:42-44; 2 Korin 2:10-11, 4:4, 11:13-15; Epasas 2:2; 1 Tesalonaika 2:18; 2 Tesalonaika 2:9-12; 1 Pita 5:8-9; 1 Yon 3:8-10; Hatanga Masok 12:7-12, 20:1-3, 20:10.
\mt3 Urana sina haringingua nakira bu tasoxauti Satan xaung tadali mauxangandi
\p Matyu 4:1-11, 6:13; Luk 22:31-32; Yon 17:14-19; Rom 8:31-39, 12:12, 16:19-20; 1 Korin 10:12-13, 16:13; 2 Korin 12:7-10; Epasas 3:20-21, 6:10-18; Pilipai 4:13; 1 Tesalonaika 3:5-8; 2 Tesalonaika 3:3; 2 Timoti 1:7-8; Hibru 2:18, 4:14-16, 12:1-2; Yems 4:7; 1 Pita 1:5, 5:8-11; 1 Yon 4:4, 5:3-5; Hatanga Masok 12:7-12.
\mt3 Bunging xumana Urana hamaringia lipu busingamdi
\p Matyu 4:23-25, 9:35, 11:2-5; Aposel 3:1-6, 8:4-8, 19:11-16, 28:8-9; 1 Korin 12:9, 12:29-30; 2 Korin 12:7-10; 1 Timoti 5:23; 2 Timoti 4:20; Yems 5:14-15.
\mt2 Baraxintadi bagula disok kimu
\mt3 Yesu bagula goxoya ma titia
